            "title": "A股半日挫  深股跌逾2.7%   創板插逾3%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股半日收跌。兩市成交合計13054.93億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250206_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250206_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指收跌73點或1.88%，報3857點，上證指數開報3896點，跌0.87%或35點，早段見3912，跌19點或0.48%，為半日高位，尾段見3840，跌91點或2.31%。半日成交5419.6億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指半日瀉352點或2.72%，開報12752點，跌1.76%或228點，最高報12812，跌168點1.29%，為半日高位，後段低見12551，瀉429點或3.31%，半日成交7635.33億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300半日跌88點或1.94%，創業板報2945點，跌96點或3.18%。</p>\n</div>",
